    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >架空地图模拟器 于壁纸中见证王朝兴衰</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款创新的模拟游戏中,您将成为架空世界的缔造者与见证者,让想象中的历史在您的日常生活中徐徐展开。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 生成或编辑自定义的架空地图,构建您独特的想象世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/7d3528f347bb3877be98bb06632521d9.poster.avif?t=1770973543\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/7d3528f347bb3877be98bb06632521d9.webm?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 模拟国家间的政治，外交、发展和战争,观察数百乃至上千年的历史演变 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/11105053ca8cc5e26ae2b0ecd9328d30.poster.avif?t=1770973543\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/11105053ca8cc5e26ae2b0ecd9328d30.webm?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/11105053ca8cc5e26ae2b0ecd9328d30.mp4?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 如你所愿，操控国家命运,塑造世界格局 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/aee93be89caf7ac182e6e1995b952346.poster.avif?t=1770973543\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/aee93be89caf7ac182e6e1995b952346.webm?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/aee93be89caf7ac182e6e1995b952346.mp4?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 独特的Windows桌面壁纸模式 - 在您工作或休息时,帝国在背景中悄然兴衰</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/e738ba352bbc31be280a49a4dc790506.poster.avif?t=1770973543\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/e738ba352bbc31be280a49a4dc790506.webm?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035500/extras/e738ba352bbc31be280a49a4dc790506.mp4?t=1770973543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您是历史爱好者、架空世界创作者,还是寻求独特桌面体验的用户,《架空地图模拟器》都能为您带来前所未有的模拟体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎各位玩家通过加入我们的官方游戏社区并关注官方账号来获取最新的游戏消息，您也可以在这些平台提供建议和反馈、分享您的作品、交流游戏心得！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >↓↓↓下为各QQ群群号↓↓↓</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【为防止新人没有名额进群，因此聊天群实行“一人一群”规则，请勿加入多个聊天群】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（最早群）一群·架空地图模拟器官方聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >630922170</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >二群·架空地图模拟器官方聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >727291484</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（最新群）三群·架空地图模拟器官方聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1065384563</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四群·架空地图模拟器官方聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >932869590</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五群·架空地图模拟器官方聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >983856528</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（人最多）六群·架空地图模拟器官方聊天群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >599786643</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆创作交流群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图交流·架地模官方图演阁：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >211955990</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MOD交流·架地模官方延举阁：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >796993241</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文字创作·架地模官方瀚文阁：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1136136169</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆互动交流群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >答疑解惑·架地模官方互助群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >834666455</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开盘组·架地模官方互动交流群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >980323200</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架地模官方文游·忒伊亚：起源：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >670772844</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆事务群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建议反馈组·架地模官方事务群</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >813979921</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >图文投稿组·架地模官方事务群</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >925393362</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中文Wiki组·架地模官方事务群</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1043171324</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆其他官方社群/账号：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ频道：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方主频道：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架空地图模拟器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >频道号：JKDTMNQFMS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瀚文阁附属频道：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架空世界观</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >频道号：JIAKONGSHIJIE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文游社群附属频道：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忒伊亚：起源</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >频道号：TEYIYAQIYUAN</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贴吧：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架空地图模拟器吧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哔哩哔哩：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架空地图模拟器官方</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UID:3546733061606375</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方邮箱：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:fantasymapsimulator@gmail.com\">fantasymapsimulator@gmail.com</a></p>",
